list.name: Test start
list.query: SELECT title,text,tags FROM "nbomber__annotations"  WHERE "title" =~ /.*started/ AND test_name=~ /$test_name/ AND $timeFilter AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/ FILL(null)

list.name: Test ended
list.query: SELECT text,title,tags FROM "nbomber__annotations"  WHERE "title" =~ /.*ended/ AND test_name=~ /$test_name/ AND $timeFilter AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/

targets.query: SELECT last("value") FROM "nbomber__ok.request.rps" WHERE test_name =~ /$test_name/ AND scenario =~ /$scenario$/ AND step =~ /$step$/ AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/ AND build_$build_source =~ /$build/ AND  $timeFilter GROUP BY scenario, step, time($__interval) FILL($fill)

targets.query:
SELECT 
last("Count - All") AS "Count - All",  
last("Count - OK") AS "Count - OK", 
last(rps) AS Rps, 
last("Latency Min") AS "Latency Min", 
last("Latency Max") AS "Latency Max", 
last("Latency Mean") AS "Latency Mean",
last("Latency p50") AS "Latency p50",
last("Latency p75") AS "Latency p75",
last("Latency p95") AS "Latency p95",
last("Latency p99") AS "Latency p99",
last("All bytes") AS "All bytes"
FROM (SELECT 
           "all" AS "Count - All",
	   count AS "Count - OK",
	   rps,
	   scenario,
	   step
FROM "nbomber__ok.summary" WHERE test_name =~ /$test_name/ AND scenario =~ /$scenario$/ AND step =~ /$step$/ AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/ AND build_$build_source =~ /$build/ AND $timeFilter AND stat_type = 'request' FILL($fill)),
(SELECT 
           min AS "Latency Min",
	   max AS "Latency Max",
	   mean AS "Latency Mean",
           percent50 AS "Latency p50",
           percent75 AS "Latency p75",
           percent95 AS "Latency p95",
           percent99 AS "Latency p99",
	   scenario,
	   step
FROM "nbomber__ok.summary" WHERE test_name =~ /$test_name/ AND scenario =~ /$scenario$/ AND step =~ /$step$/ AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/ AND build_$build_source =~ /$build/ AND $timeFilter AND stat_type = 'latency' FILL($fill)),
(SELECT 
           allbytes AS "All bytes",
	   scenario,
	   step
FROM "nbomber__ok.summary" WHERE test_name =~ /$test_name/ AND scenario =~ /$scenario$/ AND step =~ /$step$/ AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/ AND build_$build_source =~ /$build/ AND $timeFilter AND stat_type = 'datatransfer' FILL($fill)) GROUP BY scenario, step FILL($fill)

SELECT 
last("Count - All") AS "Count - All",  
last("Count - FAIL") AS "Count - FAIL", 
last(rps) AS Rps, 
last("Latency Min") AS "Latency Min",

last("Latency p50") AS "Latency p50",
last("Latency p75") AS "Latency p75",
last("Latency p95") AS "Latency p95",
last("Latency p99") AS "Latency p99",
last("All bytes") AS "All bytes"
FROM (SELECT 
           "all" AS "Count - All",
	   count AS "Count - FAIL",
	   rps,
	   scenario,
	   step
FROM "nbomber__fail.summary" WHERE test_name =~ /$test_name/ AND scenario =~ /$scenario$/ AND step =~ /$step$/ AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/ AND build_$build_source =~ /$build/ AND $timeFilter AND stat_type = 'request' FILL($fill)),
(SELECT 
           min AS "Latency Min",
	   max AS "Latency Max",
	   mean AS "Latency Mean",
           percent50 AS "Latency p50",
           percent75 AS "Latency p75",
           percent95 AS "Latency p95",
           percent99 AS "Latency p99",
	   scenario,
	   step
FROM "nbomber__fail.summary" WHERE test_name =~ /$test_name/ AND scenario =~ /$scenario$/ AND step =~ /$step$/ AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/ AND build_$build_source =~ /$build/ AND $timeFilter AND stat_type = 'latency' FILL($fill)),
(SELECT 
           allbytes AS "All bytes",
	   scenario,
	   step
FROM "nbomber__fail.summary" WHERE test_name =~ /$test_name/ AND scenario =~ /$scenario$/ AND step =~ /$step$/ AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/ AND build_$build_source =~ /$build/ AND $timeFilter AND stat_type = 'datatransfer' FILL($fill)) GROUP BY scenario, step FILL($fill)

list.label: TestName
list.name: test_name
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "nbomber__simulation.value" WITH KEY = "test_name"

list.label: Scenario
list.name: scenario
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES WITH KEY = "scenario"  WHERE test_name =~ /$test_name/ AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/

list.label: Step
list.name: step
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES WITH KEY = "step"  WHERE test_name =~ /$test_name$/ AND pipeline =~ /$pipeline/ AND scenario =~ /$scenario$/

list.label: Pipeline
list.name: pipeline
list.query: SELECT DISTINCT("pipeline") FROM (SELECT "pipeline","value" FROM "nbomber__simulation.value" WHERE test_name =~ /$test_name/)

list.label: Build source
list.name: build_source
list.query: SHOW TAG KEYS FROM "nbomber__simulation.value" WHERE test_name=~ /$test_name/

list.label: Build
list.name: build
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "nbomber__simulation.value" WITH KEY =~ /build_$build_source/ WHERE pipeline =~ /$pipeline/

list.label: Build history
list.name: build_history
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "nbomber__simulation.value" WITH KEY =~ /build_$build_source/
